     C*
     C* SELECTED ALL DOCK
B2   C           PDOCK     IFNE '    '
B3   C           PDOCK     ANDNEBANUKE
     C                     ITER
E2   C                     END
     C*
     C* SELECTED FACTORY
B2   C           PSIRK     IFNE BANKOJ
