E-02 ENTER FACTORY CODE!                                               02
E-03 DATE ENTERED IS INVALID!                                          03
E-04 CONTAINER WEIGHT SHOULD NOT BE 0!                                 04
E-05 ENTER Y OR N ONLY!                                                05
E-06 NO DATA!                                                          06
E-07 PLEASE GO TO THE MENU #999 AND SET THE NUMBER OF PACKING LIST!    07
E-08 PRINTER SELECTION ERROR!                                          08
E-09 DELIVERY CODE DOES NOT EXIST IN PACKING LIST MASTER <AB#C90>!     09
PRESS F5 TO PROCESS...                                                 10
E-11 ENTER BIN# !                                                      11
E-12 ENTER SHIP DATE!                                                  12
E-13 ENTER DOCK CODE!                                                  13
E-14 ALL "N" NOT ALLOWED!                                              14
                                                                       15
** CMD(70A) ..+... 2 ...+... 3 ...+... 4 ...+... 5 ...+... 6 ...+... 7
CLRPFM QTEMP/ABWPP31
